            <div class="alert alert-success" id="recent-changes">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">📝 Recent Changes (v0.03 - Jan 11, 2026)</h3>
                <p><strong>Version Consolidation Update:</strong> Consolidated from v1.00 to v0.03. All database schema relationships verified against HEAD. Verification workflow and user association methods confirmed current.</p>
                <p><strong>Previous v1.00 Changes (Jan 9, 2026):</strong></p>
                <ul style="margin: 5px 0 0 20px;">
                    <li><strong>Initial Documentation:</strong> Created comprehensive documentation for WebSearchResult model</li>
                    <li><strong>Verification Workflow:</strong> Documented multi-state verification system (pending/verified/rejected)</li>
